1153080,204,212,2,10,1,70,8,Ayaṃ pana kammavācā tathāgatassa parinibbānato ekavīsatime divase katā. 
1153081,204,212,11,34,1,106,10,Vuttañhetaṃ dīghanikāyaṭṭhakathāyaṃ( dī. ni. aṭṭha.1. paṭhamasaṅgītikathā)‘‘ ayaṃ pana kammavācā tathāgatassa parinibbānato ekavīsatime divase katā. 
1153082,204,212,35,47,1,118,11,"Bhagavā hi visākhapuṇṇamāyaṃ paccūsasamaye parinibbuto, athassa sattāhaṃ suvaṇṇavaṇṇaṃ sarīraṃ gandhamālādīhi pūjayiṃsu. "
1153083,204,212,48,53,1,43,5,Evaṃ sattāhaṃ sādhukīḷanadivasā nāma ahesuṃ. 
1153084,204,212,54,69,1,125,14,"Tato sattāhaṃ citakāya agginā jhāyi, sattāhaṃ sattipañjaraṃ katvā santhāgārasālāyaṃ dhātupūjaṃ kariṃsūti ekavīsati divasā gatā. "
1153085,204,212,70,74,1,55,4,Jeṭṭhamūlasukkapakkhapañcamiyaṃ pana dhātuyo bhājayiṃsu. 
1153086,204,212,75,90,1,167,15,Etasmiṃ dhātubhājanadivase sannipatitassa mahābhikkhusaṅghassa subhaddena vuḍḍhapabbajitena kataṃ anācāraṃ ārocetvā vuttanayeneva bhikkhū uccinitvā ayaṃ kammavācā katā. 
1153087,204,212,91,143,1,342,46,"Imañca pana kammavācaṃ katvā thero bhikkhū āmantesi‘ āvuso idāni tumhākaṃ cattālīsadivasā okāso, tato paraṃ ayaṃ nāma no palibodho atthīti vattuṃ na labbhā, tasmā etthantare yassa rogapalibodho vā ācariyupajjhāyapalibodho vā mātāpitupalibodho vā atthi, pattaṃ vā pana pacitabbaṃ cīvaraṃ vā kātabbaṃ, so taṃ palibodhaṃ chinditvā karaṇīyaṃ karotū’ ti. "
1153088,204,212,144,169,1,190,23,"Evañca pana vatvā thero attano pañcasatāya parisāya parivuto rājagahaṃ gato, aññepi mahātherā attano attano parivāraṃ gahetvā sokasallasamappitaṃ mahājanaṃ assāsetukāmā taṃ taṃ disaṃ pakkantā. "
