1154808,204,593,46,49,1,28,2,{Ekaladdhike}ti samānaladdhike. 
1154809,204,593,50,54,1,27,4,Kiṃ vadati sīlenāti kiṃvādī. 
1154810,204,593,55,66,1,56,10,"Atha vā ko katamo vādo kiṃvādo, so etassa atthīti kiṃvādī. "
1154811,204,593,67,74,1,68,7,Sassataṃ attānañca lokañca vadanti paññapenti sīlenāti sassatavādino. 
1154812,204,593,75,84,1,54,8,"Atha vā vadanti etenāti vādo, diṭṭhiyā etaṃ adhivacanaṃ. "
1154813,204,593,85,96,1,80,9,"Sassato vādo sassatavādo, so etesaṃ atthīti sassatavādino, sassatadiṭṭhinoti attho. "
1154814,204,593,97,113,1,95,14,"Atha sassato vādo etesamatthīti kasmā vuttaṃ, tesañhi attā loko ca sassatoti adhippeto, na vādoti? "
1154815,204,593,114,115,1,10,1,Saccametaṃ. 
1154816,204,593,116,129,1,74,9,Sassatasahacaritatāya pana vādopi sassatoti vutto yathā‘‘ kuntā pacarantī’’ ti. 
1154817,204,593,130,136,1,49,6,Sassatoti vādo etesanti vā itisaddalopo daṭṭhabbo. 
1154818,204,593,137,155,1,123,17,"Ye rūpādīsu aññataraṃ attāti ca lokoti ca gahetvā taṃ sassataṃ amataṃ niccaṃ dhuvaṃ paññapenti, te sassatavādinoti veditabbā. "
1154819,204,593,156,159,1,37,3,Vuttañhetaṃ niddese paṭisambhidāyañca–
1154820,204,594,2,15,1,65,11,‘ ‘ Rūpaṃ attā ceva loko ca sassato cāti attānañca lokañca paññapenti. 
1154821,204,594,16,35,1,95,14,Vedanaṃ… saññaṃ… saṅkhāre… viññāṇaṃ attā ceva loko ca sassato cāti attānañca lokañca paññapentī’’ ti. 
1154822,204,595,2,27,1,145,17,"Ayañca attho‘‘ rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, vedanaṃ… saññaṃ… saṅkhāre… viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassatī’’ ti imissā pañcavidhāya sakkāyadiṭṭhiyā vasena vutto."
1154823,204,595,28,55,1,164,19,‘‘ Rūpavantaṃ attānan’’ tiādikāya pana pañcadasavidhāya sakkāyadiṭṭhiyā vasena cattāro cattāro khandhe‘‘ attā’’ ti gahetvā tadañño lokoti paññapentīti ayañca attho labbhati. 
1154824,204,595,56,87,1,165,22,"Tathā ekaṃ khandhaṃ‘‘ attā’’ ti gahetvā añño attano upabhogabhūto lokoti, sasantatipatite vā khandhe‘‘ attā’’ ti gahetvā tadañño lokoti paññapentīti evamettha attho veditabbo. "
1154825,204,595,88,97,1,79,8,"Sattesu saṅkhāresu vā ekaccaṃ sassataṃ etassāti ekaccasassato, ekaccasassatavādo. "
1154826,204,595,98,103,1,52,4,"So etesamatthīti ekaccasassatikā, ekaccasassatavādino. "
1154827,204,595,104,110,1,61,5,Te duvidhā honti sattekaccasassatikā saṅkhārekaccasassatikāti . 
1154828,204,595,111,128,1,99,12,"Tattha‘‘ issaro nicco, aññe sattā aniccā’’ ti evaṃ pavattavādā sattekaccasassatikā seyyathāpi issaravādā."
1154829,204,595,129,144,1,84,10,"‘‘ Nicco brahmā, aññe sattā aniccā’’ ti evaṃ pavattavādāpi sattekaccasassatikāti veditabbā."
1154830,204,595,145,160,1,105,10,"‘‘ Paramāṇavo niccā, dviaṇukādayo aniccā’’ ti evaṃ pavattavādā saṅkhārekaccasassatikā seyyathāpi kaṇādavādādayo."
1154831,204,595,161,174,1,84,8,"‘‘ Cakkhādayo aniccā, viññāṇaṃ niccan’’ ti evaṃvādinopi saṅkhārekaccasassatikāti veditabbā. "
1154832,204,596,2,24,1,152,16,"Nanu ‘‘ ekacce dhammā sassatā, ekacce asassatā’’ ti etasmiṃ vāde cakkhādīnaṃ asassatabhāvasanniṭṭhānaṃ yathāsabhāvāvabodho eva, tayidaṃ kathaṃ micchādassananti? "
1154833,204,596,25,28,1,13,3,Ko vā evamāha–
1154834,204,596,29,45,1,135,11,"‘‘ cakkhādīnaṃ asassatabhāvasanniṭṭhānaṃ micchādassanan’’ ti, asassatesuyeva pana kesañci dhammānaṃ sassatabhāvābhiniveso idha micchādassanaṃ. "
1154835,204,596,46,64,1,196,16,"Tena pana ekavāre pavattamānena cakkhādīnaṃ asassatabhāvāvabodho vidūsito saṃsaṭṭhabhāvato, visasaṃsaṭṭho viya sabbo sappimaṇḍo sakiccakaraṇāsamatthatāya sammādassanapakkhe ṭhapetabbataṃ nārahatīti. "
1154836,204,596,65,78,1,146,13,Asassatabhāvena nicchitāpi vā cakkhuādayo samāropitajīvasabhāvā eva diṭṭhigatikehi gayhantīti tadavabodhassa micchādassanabhāvo na sakkā nivāretuṃ. 
1154837,204,596,79,104,1,240,24,"Evañca katvā asaṅkhatāya ca saṅkhatāya ca dhātuyā vasena yathākkamaṃ ekacce dhammā sassatā, ekacce asassatāti evaṃ pavatto vibhajjavādopi ekaccasassatavādo āpajjatīti evaṃpakārā codanā anavakāsā hoti aviparītadhammasabhāvasampaṭipattibhāvato. "
1154838,204,596,105,121,1,171,15,"Kāmañcettha purimasassatavādepi asassatānaṃ dhammānaṃ sassatāti gahaṇaṃ visesato micchādassanaṃ, sassatānaṃ pana sassatāti gāho na micchādassanaṃ yathāsabhāvaggahaṇabhāvato. "
1154839,204,596,122,133,1,114,11,Asassatesuyeva pana kecideva dhammā sassatāti gahetabbadhammesu vibhāgappavattiyā imassa vādassa vādantaratā vuttā. 
1154840,204,596,134,147,1,169,13,Na cettha samudāyantogadhattā ekadesassa sappadesasassataggāho nippadesasassataggāhe samodhānaṃ gacchatīti sakkā vattuṃ vāditabbisayavisesavasena vādadvayassa pavattattā. 
1154841,204,596,148,170,1,165,17,"Aññe eva hi diṭṭhigatikā‘‘ sabbe dhammā sassatā’’ ti abhiniviṭṭhā, aññe ekaccasassatāti saṅkhārānaṃ anavasesapariyādānaṃ ekadesapariggaho ca vādadvayassa paribyattoyevāti. "
1154842,204,597,2,13,1,71,9,"{Antānantikā}ti ettha amati gacchati ettha sabhāvo osānanti anto, mariyādā. "
1154843,204,597,14,16,1,21,2,Tappaṭisedhena ananto. 
1154844,204,597,17,20,1,25,3,Kassa panāyaṃ antānantoti? 
1154845,204,597,21,37,1,158,15,"Lokīyati saṃsāranissaraṇatthikehi diṭṭhigatikehi, lokīyati vā ettha tehi puññāpuññaṃ tabbipāko cāti lokoti saṅkhyaṃ gatassa paṭibhāganimittādisabhāvassa attano. "
1154846,204,597,38,60,1,132,16,"Anto ca ananto ca antānanto ca nevantanānanto cāti antānanto sāmaññaniddesena, ekasesena vā‘‘ nāmarūpapaccayā saḷāyatanan’’ tiādīsu viya. "
1154847,204,597,61,72,1,59,7,Antānantasahacarito vādo antānanto yathā‘‘ kuntā pacarantī’’ ti. 
1154848,204,597,73,84,1,55,7,Antānantasannissayo vā yathā‘‘ mañcā ukkuṭṭhiṃ karontī’’ ti. 
1154849,204,597,85,90,1,44,4,"So etesamatthīti antānantikā, antānantavādino."
1154850,204,597,91,128,1,185,30,"‘‘ Antavā ayaṃ loko, ananto ayaṃ loko, antavā ca ayaṃ loko ananto ca, nevāyaṃ loko antavā na panānanto’’ ti evaṃ antaṃ vā anantaṃ vā antānantaṃ vā nevantanānantaṃ vā ārabbha pavattavādāti attho. "
1154851,204,597,129,137,1,84,7,Catubbidhā hi antānantavādino antavādī anantavādī antānantavādī nevantanānantavādīti. 
1154852,204,597,138,155,1,106,13,Tathā hi koci paṭibhāganimittaṃ cakkavāḷapariyantaṃ avaḍḍhetvā taṃ‘‘ loko’’ ti gahetvā antasaññī lokasmiṃ hoti. 
1154853,204,597,156,162,1,62,6,Cakkavāḷapariyantaṃ katvā vaḍḍhitakasiṇe pana anantasaññī hoti. 
1154854,204,597,163,173,1,90,10,Uddhamadho avaḍḍhetvā pana tiriyaṃ vaḍḍhetvā uddhamadho antasaññī tiriyaṃ anantasaññī hoti. 
1154855,204,597,174,188,1,112,13,"Koci pana yasmā lokasaññito attā adhigatavisesehi mahesīhi kadāci ananto sakkhidiṭṭho anusuyyati, tasmā nevantavā. "
1154856,204,597,189,205,1,119,15,"Yasmā pana tehiyeva kadāci antavā sakkhidiṭṭho anusuyyati, tasmā na pana anantoti evaṃ nevantanānantasaññī lokasmiṃ hoti. "
1154857,204,597,206,217,1,93,10,"Keci pana yadi panāyaṃ attā antavāsiyā, dūradese upapajjamānānussaraṇādikiccanipphatti na siyā. "
1154858,204,597,218,225,1,73,7,Atha ananto idha ṭhitassa devalokanirayādīsu sukhadukkhānubhavanampi siyā. 
1154859,204,597,226,246,1,162,18,"Sace pana antavā ca ananto ca, tadubhayapaṭisedhadosasamāyogo, tasmā antavā anantoti ca abyākaraṇīyo attāti evaṃ takkanavasena nevantanānantasaññī hotīti vaṇṇayanti. "
1154860,204,598,2,22,1,199,19,"Ettha ca yuttaṃ tāva purimānaṃ tiṇṇaṃ vādīnaṃ antañca anantañca antānantañca ārabbha pavattavādattā antānantikattaṃ, pacchimassa pana tadubhayapaṭisedhanavasena pavattavādattā kathaṃ antānantikattanti? "
1154861,204,598,23,26,1,45,3,Tadubhayapaṭisedhanavasena pavattavādattā eva. 
1154862,204,598,27,34,1,72,7,Yasmā antānantapaasedhavādopi antānantavisayo eva taṃ ārabbha pavattattā. 
1154863,204,598,35,65,1,221,23,"Etadatthameva hi ārabbha‘‘ pavattavādā’’ ti heṭṭhā vuttaṃ, evaṃ santepi yuttaṃ tāva pacchimavādadvayassa antānantikattaṃ, antānantānaṃ vasena ubhayavisayattā etesaṃ vādassa, purimavādadvayassa pana kathaṃ visuṃ antānantikattanti? "
1154864,204,598,66,67,1,14,1,Upacāravuttiyā. 
