1154866,204,599,2,10,1,57,7,{Amarāvikkhepikā}ti ettha na marati na upacchijjatīti amarā. 
1154867,204,599,11,13,1,5,2,Kā sā?
1154868,204,599,14,57,1,155,25,"‘‘ Evantipi me no, tathātipi me no, aññathātipi me no, notipi me no, no notipi me no’’ ti( dī. ni.1.62) evaṃ pavattavādavasena pariyantarahitā diṭṭhigatikassa diṭṭhi ceva vācā ca."
1154869,204,599,58,84,1,162,19,"‘‘ Evantipi me no’’ tiādinā vividho nānappakāro khepo paravādīnaṃ khipanaṃ vikkhepo, amarāya diṭṭhiyā vācāya vā vikkhepo amarāvikkhepo, so etesamatthīti amarāvikkhepikā. "
1154870,204,599,85,96,1,97,10,"Atha vā amarāya diṭṭhiyā vācāya vikkhipantīti amarāvikkhepino, amarāvikkhepino eva amarāvikkhepikā. "
1154871,204,599,97,130,1,239,30,"Atha vā amarā nāma macchajāti, sā ummujjananimujjanādivasena udake sandhāvamānā gahetuṃ na sakkā, evameva ayampi vādo ekasmiṃ sabhāve anavaṭṭhānato ito cito ca sandhāvati, gāhaṃ na upagacchatīti amarāya vikkhepo viyāti amarāvikkhepoti vuccati. "
1154872,204,599,131,152,1,82,13,Ayañhi amarāvikkhepiko‘‘ idaṃ kusalan’’ ti vā‘‘ akusalan’’ ti vā puṭṭho na kiñci byākaroti.
1154873,204,599,153,171,1,50,10,‘‘ Idaṃ kusalan’’ ti vā puṭṭho‘‘ evantipi me no’’ ti vadati. 
1154874,204,599,172,190,1,52,10,Tato‘‘ kiṃ akusalan’’ ti vutte‘‘ tathātipi me no’’ ti vadati.
1154875,204,599,191,209,1,59,10,‘‘ Kiṃ ubhayato aññathā’’ tipi vutte‘‘ aññathātipi me no’’ ti vadati. 
1154876,204,599,210,233,1,70,14,"Tato‘‘ tividhenapi na hoti, kiṃ te laddhī’’ ti vutte‘‘ notipi me no’’ ti vadati. "
1154877,204,599,234,256,1,59,14,Tato‘‘ kiṃ no no te laddhī’’ ti vutte‘‘ no notipi me no’’ ti vadati. 
1154878,204,599,257,265,1,59,7,"Evaṃ vikkhepameva āpajjati, ekamekasmimpi pakkhe na tiṭṭhati. "
1154879,204,599,266,283,1,84,12,"Tato‘‘ atthi paro loko’’ tiādinā puṭṭhopi evameva vikkhipati, na ekasmiṃ pakkhe tiṭṭhati. "
1154880,204,599,284,289,1,59,5,So vuttappakāro amarāvikkhepo etesamatthīti amarāvikkhepikā. 
1154881,204,600,2,23,1,196,20,"Nanu cāyaṃ sabbopi amarāvikkhepiko kusalādayo dhamme paralokatthikādīni ca yathābhūtaṃ anavabujjhamāno tattha tattha pañhaṃ puṭṭho pucchāya vikkhepanamattaṃ āpajjati, tassa kathaṃ diṭṭhigatikabhāvo. "
1154882,204,600,24,33,1,91,9,Na hi avattukāmassa viya pucchitaṃ ajānantassa vikkhepakaraṇamattena diṭṭhigatikatā yuttāti? 
