1154884,204,600,49,68,1,216,19,Micchābhiniviṭṭhoyeva hi puggalo mandabuddhitāya kusalādidhamme paralokatthikādīni ca yāthāvato asampaṭipajjamāno attanā aviññātassa atthassa paraṃ viññāpetuṃ asakkuṇeyyatāya musāvādādibhayena ca vikkhepaṃ āpajjatīti. 
