1155026,204,625,37,66,1,203,23,"Rājā pana tesaṃ sabbajeṭṭhakassa asokakumārassa uparajjaṭṭhānañca avantiraṭṭhañca datvā athekadivasaṃ attano upaṭṭhānaṃ āgataṃ disvā‘‘ tāta, uparāja, tava raṭṭhaṃ gantvā tattha ujjenīnagare vasāhī’’ ti āṇāpesi. "
1155027,204,625,67,101,1,309,34,So pitu vacanena taṃ ujjeniṃ gacchanto antarāmagge veṭisagirinagare veṭisanāmakassa seṭṭhissa ghare nivāsaṃ upagantvā tassa seṭṭhissa dhītaraṃ lakkhaṇasampannaṃ yobbanappattaṃ veṭisagiriṃ nāma kumāriṃ disvā tāya paṭibaddhacitto mātāpitūnaṃ kathāpetvā taṃ tehi dinnaṃ paṭilabhitvā tāya saddhiṃ saṃvāsaṃ kappesi. 
1155028,204,625,102,112,1,77,10,Sā tena saṃvāsena sañjātagabbhā hutvā tato ujjeniṃ nītā mahindakumāraṃ janayi. 
