1156764,204,980,10,35,1,171,21,"Tathā hi anuppanne buddhe titthāyatane pabbajitā vāyokasiṇe parikammaṃ katvā catutthajjhānaṃ nibbattetvā tato vuṭṭhāya‘‘ dhī cittaṃ, dhī cittaṃ, cittassa nāma abhāvoyeva sādhu. "
