1158552,204,1324,2,33,1,103,11,"So ( ma. ni. aṭṭha.1.89; dha. sa. aṭṭha. akusalakammapathakathā) ca pāṇātipāto guṇavirahitesu tiracchānagatādīsu pāṇesu khuddake pāṇe appasāvajjo, mahante mahāsāvajjo. "
