1159101,204,1396,15,26,1,97,7,‘‘ Sotāpattiphalasamāpattatthāyā’’ tiādīsu catūsu phalavāresu pana appaṇihitaphalasamāpatti veditabbā. 
1159102,204,1396,27,28,1,5,1,Kasmā? 
1159103,204,1396,29,36,1,110,7,Suññatavihārasamāpattatthāya animittavihārasamāpattatthāyāti itarāsaṃ dvinnaṃ phalasamāpattīnaṃ visuṃ vuttattā. 
