1159577,204,1454,82,130,1,405,41,"Yathā hi so asaññasattā cavitvā idhūpapanno pabbajito samāno abhiññālābhī hutvā pubbenivāsaṃ anussaranto idhūpapattimeva disvā tato paraṃ asaññabhave uppattiṃ anussaritumasakkonto‘‘ ahaṃ adhiccasamuppanno pubbe nāhosiṃ, somhi etarahi ahutvā sattatāya pariṇato, sesāpi sattā tādisāyevā’’ ti abhinavasattapātubhāvadiṭṭhiṃ gaṇhāti, evamayampi upapātamattameva disvā cutiṃ apassanto navasattapātubhāvadiṭṭhiṃ gaṇhāti. "
