1159997,204,1531,2,4,1,15,2,Aparampi vuttaṃ–
1159998,204,1532,2,49,1,339,38,"‘ ‘ Atha kho sakko devānamindo asītiyā devatāsahassehi saddhiṃ yenāyasmā mahāmoggallāno tenupasaṅkami… pe… ekamantaṃ ṭhitaṃ kho sakkaṃ devānamindaṃ āyasmā mahāmoggallāno etadavoca‘ sādhu kho, devānaminda, buddhasaraṇagamanaṃ hoti, buddhasaraṇagamanahetu kho, devānaminda, evamidhekacce sattā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjanti. "
1159999,204,1532,50,82,1,154,20,Te aññe deve dasahi ṭhānehi adhigaṇhanti dibbena āyunā dibbena vaṇṇena sukhena yasena ādhipateyyena dibbehi rūpehi saddehi gandhehi rasehi phoṭṭhabbehī’’’ ti( saṃ. ni.4.341). 
1160000,204,1533,2,7,1,25,5,Esa nayo dhamme saṅghe ca. 
